text: Avry is a municipality of the district Saane in the canton of Fribourg in Switzerland. The municipality was created on 1 January 2001, when the municipalities of Avry-sur-Matran and Corjolens joined together to become Avry.Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz published by the Swiss Federal Statistical Office accessed 19 July 2011 == Gallery == AVRY.JPG|Avry Corjolens vue du village.jpg|Corjolens Chapelle-sainte-trinite-avry.jpg|The chapel of Sainte Trinit√© at Avry == References == == Other websites == * Official website * * Category:Municipalities in Sarine
